title: these s requirements
body: im not really mad just highkey confused, 25 mins as trynda jg and i have 178 cs i was 14/3/7 and i only got an s-? i swear any other jger i woulda got an s+ for that

replies.body:
It has nothing to do with what other junglers get.

Your grade is based on how you played compared to other people of the same rough MMR playing the same champion and role, and it is based more on contribution, gold, objectives, vision than KDA.
